ow its applicability to\nSchr\\\"odinger-type operators in $L^2(\\mathbb{R}^n)$.\n  Extensions to second-order (locally uniformly) elliptic differential\noperators on $\\mathbb{R}^n$ with a possibly strongly singular potential\ncoefficient are treated as well.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 5 Sep 2015 23:43:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 20 Aug 2016 12:45:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-23"}
